# NOTE: web/dist/ is intentionally committed — it is embedded into the GUI binary
# via //go:embed all:dist in web/embed.go, so a clean `go build`/`go install`
# works without Node. The explicit un-ignore below makes any future accidental
# `dist/` rule a no-op for the embedded directory.
!web/dist/

